+### Prometheus scrape target (exporter)
+
+If you use the standalone exporter `of-inputs-v3-circuit-exporter` (port 9164), add a scrape job:
+
+```yaml
+scrape_configs:
+  - job_name: of_inputs_v3_circuit
+    static_configs:
